headline.print_headline: Ledecky Beats Franklin in 200 Free at US Nationals
headline.main: Ledecky Beats Franklin in 200 Free at US Nationals

lead_paragraph: Katie Ledecky beat defending champion Missy Franklin to win the 200-meter freestyle in a showdown of teen swimming queens Thursday night at the U.S. national championships. Franklin returned 75 minutes later to win the 200 backstroke.
